<pb n="1a"/>
說文解字通釋卷第二十八<lb/>
　　　　　　　　　繫傳二十八<lb/>
　　　　文林郎守秘書省校書郎臣徐鍇傳釋<lb/>
　　　　朝散大夫行祕書省校書郎臣朱?反切<lb/>
　　四十二部　文　重<lb/>
<hi>小<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>也象形凡<graphic n="KR0935" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0935.png" mimeType="image/png"/>之?皆?<graphic n="KR0935" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0935.png" mimeType="image/png"/>臣鍇曰再尸象推之漸進也都魁反危高也?<graphic n="KR0935" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0935.png" mimeType="image/png"/>屮?讀若/臣鍇曰?字?此知舌反/吏事君也???<graphic n="KR0935" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0935.png" mimeType="image/png"/>/<graphic n="KR0935" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0935.png" mimeType="image/png"/>猶?也此與師同<pb n="1b"/>意臣鍇曰按國語天子千品萬官也?在屋下也師?<graphic n="KR0935" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0935.png" mimeType="image/png"/>亦取義于?也?意古安反</hi>
　　　　　文三<lb/>
<hi>大陸山無石也象形凡<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>之?皆?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>臣鍇曰彌高大也故?三尸符九反古文<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>/大<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>/夌?力膺反/大<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>/鯀?胡本反/地理也?
                        <graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>力?臣鍇曰地之脈/理也泐字?此郎忒反/闇也水之南山之北也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>??臣鍇曰山北水南日所不及都吟反/高明也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>/易?猶良反/?平地?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>/坴?栗菊反/?文陸如此大陵曰阿?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>可?一/曰阿曲<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>也?何反/阪也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>皮?一曰沱也彼移反<pb n="2a"/>坡者曰阪?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>反?一曰澤/障也一曰山脅也福?反/阪隅也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>取?臣鍇按山海經曰海?西北陬側丘反/陬也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>禺/?元無反/阻難也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>/僉?香貶反/阻也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>??一曰門榍侯?反/險也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>且/?側所反/?隗高也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>隹?臣鍇曰京高立也特賄反?隗也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>/鬼?魚賄反/高也一曰石也?/<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>允?與?反/磊也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>/<graphic n="KR1136" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1136.png" mimeType="image/png"/>?落?反?也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>肖?臣鍇曰高竦/也太玄曰豊牆阯七肖反/?高也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>??蘇狗反仰也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>登/?徒?反/?陜也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>/??勒豆反/隘也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>夾下夾反登也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>/?竹力反/古文陟/如此/高下也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>??/一曰陟寒蘸反/阪下湮也<pb n="2b"/>?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>??/似集反/也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>區/??于反/下隊也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>/??徒崔反/?高墮也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>??臣鍇曰?隊/字本無土也徒佩反/下也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>?/?艮巷反/?高下也/?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>員?易曰有隕自天雨牝反/小崩也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>也?臣鍇按左思/吳都賦曰崩巒?岑池倚反/危也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>?毀省徐巡臣為<graphic n="KR2419" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR2419.png" mimeType="image/png"/>?也賈侍中說<graphic n="KR2419" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR2419.png" mimeType="image/png"/>法度也班/固說<graphic n="KR2419" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR2419.png" mimeType="image/png"/>不安也周書邦之阢<graphic n="KR2419" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR2419.png" mimeType="image/png"/>讀若虹蜺之蜺語挈反敗城<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>曰隓?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>/?臣鍇曰今俗作墮許規反臣/次立按徐鉉曰說文無字蓋二左也?力左之故?二左/篆文隓/如此/仄也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>頃/?屈呈反/落也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>多?圖坐反閬也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>亢?臣鍇曰阬閬高大而空楚辭曰導帝之乎九阬九州也此亦阬塹字看浪反<pb n="3a"/>通溝臣防水也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>/賣?讀若洞?谷反/古文<graphic n="KR2902" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR2902.png" mimeType="image/png"/>/?谷/隄也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>方?臣鍇按春秋左氏傳塹防門而守之浮長反/防或/?土/塘也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>是/?的齊反/基也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>止?只耳反阯或/?土/山?坎也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>巠?臣鍇按?雅/山?陘注連?也堅經反附婁小土山也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>巠?春秋傳/婁/無松?臣鍇曰今左傳作培假借?經切/秦謂陵阪/曰阺?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>
                    氐?臣鍇曰古言隴阺的米反/石山載土也?/<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>几?五忽反/崖也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>兼?讀若儼牛檢反塞也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>?/?晏索反/障也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>鬲/?溝厄反/隔也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>童?止向反蔽也從<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>?/?依謹反/水隈崖也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>/??嘔報反/水曲隩也?/<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>畏?千枚<pb n="3b"/>反商小塊也?臾<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>臣/鍇曰遣字?此溪善反/水衡官谷也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>解?一曰小谿臣鍇曰古亦言荅/也猴豸反/天水大阪也?/<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>龍??恐反/酒泉天?阪?/<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>衣?于機反弘農陜也虢國王季之子所封也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>夾?收儼反/弘農陜東陬也?/<graphic n="KR0671" url="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0671.png" mimeType="image/png"/>無?文區反河東安邑陬也?<graphic n="KR0671" url="h